<text top="727" left="122" width="146" height="14" font="1">The situation in Angola</text>
<text top="763" left="153" width="675" height="14" font="1">Report of the Secretary-General on the United Nations Angola Verification Mission (UNAVEM III) (S/1995/842)</text>
